name: Dev Up
tagline: Community of Indian Programmers and Hackers
body:
Dev Up is community of Indian Programmers and Hackers. Currently we have an active [slack team](https://dev-s.slack.com) and a service called [Nightreads](http://nightreads.devup.in/). 


* To join our [slack team](https://dev-s.slack.com), request your invite [here](http://slack.devup.in).
* Subscribe to [Nightreads](http://nightreads.devup.in/).
* Follow us on [Twitter](https://twitter.com/devupin).
